[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "住民Ａ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ふう……助かりました。\n皆さん、薬をありがとうございます",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "住民Ｂ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "キノコが生えてしまった人は、栄養を吸われたのか\nまだ起きていないが……あとは俺たちで面倒を見るよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ええ。お大事にね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "目的の美術品収集家も寝込んでるみたいだね。\n回復を待つしかないか",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "突然変異したキノコの魔物が島を埋め尽くそうと\nするなんて、想像以上の異常事態だったね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "ピルッツァは諸島同盟の外。\n緊急連絡網が機能しない。大惨事寸前だった",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "本当に間に合ってよかった……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "レスナたちも体調が戻ったみたいだし、\n宿に入れてもらって、しばらく町の復興を手伝いましょ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（あれからしばらくして……みんなすっかり\n　元気になったみたい。子どもたちも走り回って……）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（ああやって、みんなで遊ぶの、いいな……\n　私も、ああいう輪の中に入ってみたい……）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（でも、どうやって声をかければ……）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "……あ、あの",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "子どもＡ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "やべ！　もうこんな時間か！\n母ちゃんに店を手伝えって言われてたの忘れてた！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "子どもＢ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "私も、お勉強をしないと……またね！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "あ……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "……行っちゃいましたね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "ひゃっ！　も、もしかして、今の、見て……？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん。キューンちゃんの気持ち、分かるなあ。\n私も昔は――",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "ッ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "キューンちゃん！？\n……うう、失敗しちゃったかな。声のかけ方",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "なんだか昔の私を思い出すなあ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "……私にとってのイザナちゃんみたいな子が、\nキューンちゃんにも見つかるといいな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]